race.comment: VAREJAO (7) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in six of eight overall and strikes a very winnable contest here. Has placed five from seven over this sprint journey and should be going close to shedding the maiden tag against this lot. CARBONARA (10) got up to Listed level when last in work and will be fitter for that first-up effort in town. Include in calculations. MR DEMOCRAT (5) resumes here but showed enough in his first campaign to warrant some consideration in a race like this. Can run a race at odds. EGYPTIAN GODDESS (16) will be at peak fitness now and may earn some minor money in a race decimated by scratchings.
